node.text:
The best swim bottom in the world. The designer is this lady named Ciera. She's pretty cool and really nice. I was there when she made the first sample and I couldn't believe the fit was so perfect on every woman who tried it on. The low cut and high waist is so flattering. She's so talented. Someone should really tell her 🥸 
Available at @shopbabes
